516
00:53:07,080 --> 00:53:08,110
Chaim Rozenfeld!

517
00:53:10,020 --> 00:53:14,180
You have loved me since I was a little
girl in pigtails and after these

518
00:53:14,240 --> 00:53:17,090
many years you know very well

519
00:53:17,150 --> 00:53:21,070
an opinion from me
is not a suggestion.

520
00:53:40,200 --> 00:53:44,080
Next time,
when you come she will be prepared.

521
00:53:45,110 --> 00:53:48,100
Irena, the Underground knows
what you're doing.

522
00:53:48,160 --> 00:53:49,210
They want to help.

523
00:53:50,020 --> 00:53:53,030
